This paper discusses the concept of redundancy in biological and artificial systems to improve system performance. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-category of systems and control (cs.SY), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV).
